---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="美食地图 - 盐色运城" description="运城美食地图——羊肉泡、大盘鸡、稷山麻花、闻喜煮饼、解州羊肉泡馍等地道美味。">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-ink mb-4">美食地图</h1>
      <p class="text-stone max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">黄河岸边的烟火气，运城的每一口都是历史的滋味</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <article class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-white border border-salt-dark/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="aspect-[16/10] bg-gradient-to-br from-amber/30 to-salt-dark/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-stone/50 text-sm">羊肉泡馍</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-2">解州羊肉泡馍</h2>
          <p class="text-stone text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">运城的招牌美食，汤汁浓郁，羊肉鲜嫩，馍块吸满汤汁后香气四溢。关帝庙附近的老店最为正宗。</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-brick/10 text-brick text-xs rounded">必吃</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-amber/10 text-amber-dark text-xs rounded">盐湖区</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-white border border-salt-dark/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="aspect-[16/10] bg-gradient-to-br from-brick/20 to-salt-pink/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-stone/50 text-sm">大盘鸡</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-2">运城大盘鸡</h2>
          <p class="text-stone text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">融合了山西面食文化与西北风味的独特美食，鸡肉嫩滑，土豆软糯，拌上面条令人回味无穷。</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-brick/10 text-brick text-xs rounded">人气</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-amber/10 text-amber-dark text-xs rounded">市区</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-white border border-salt-dark/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="aspect-[16/10] bg-gradient-to-br from-pool/20 to-amber/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-stone/50 text-sm">稷山麻花</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-2">稷山麻花</h2>
          <p class="text-stone text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">山西四大名吃之一，色泽金黄，酥脆可口。相传始于隋朝，距今已有千年历史。</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-amber/10 text-amber-dark text-xs rounded">小吃</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-amber/10 text-amber-dark text-xs rounded">稷山县</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-white border border-salt-dark/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="aspect-[16/10] bg-gradient-to-br from-salt-pink/30 to-amber/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-stone/50 text-sm">闻喜煮饼</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-2">闻喜煮饼</h2>
          <p class="text-stone text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">运城传统糕点，外裹芝麻，内有栗色馅料，甜而不腻。鲁迅先生曾在《孤独者》中提及此美味。</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-amber/10 text-amber-dark text-xs rounded">糕点</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-amber/10 text-amber-dark text-xs rounded">闻喜县</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-white border border-salt-dark/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="aspect-[16/10] bg-gradient-to-br from-salt-dark/20 to-pool/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-stone/50 text-sm">北相羊肉胡卜</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-2">北相羊肉胡卜</h2>
          <p class="text-stone text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">以死面饼丝为主料，配羊肉汤煮制而成。饼丝筋道，汤鲜味美，是当地人早餐的首选。</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-amber/10 text-amber-dark text-xs rounded">早餐</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-amber/10 text-amber-dark text-xs rounded">北相镇</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-white border border-salt-dark/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="aspect-[16/10] bg-gradient-to-br from-amber/20 to-brick/10 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-stone/50 text-sm">盐湖特色小吃</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-2">盐湖黑泥养生宴</h2>
          <p class="text-stone text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">以运城盐湖黑泥入菜，独具特色。黑泥富含矿物质，是当地特色的养生美食体验。</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-pool/10 text-pool text-xs rounded">特色</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-amber/10 text-amber-dark text-xs rounded">盐湖区</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
